ensemble = construct_textbook_ensemble()
ex_rxns = [rxn.id for rxn in ensemble.base_model.reactions if rxn.id.
    startswith('EX')]
fva_fluxes = ensemble_fva(ensemble, reaction_list=ex_rxns)
rows = fva_fluxes.shape[0]
columns = fva_fluxes.shape[1]
assert rows == len(ensemble.members) * 2
assert columns == len(ex_rxns) + 1
